 {\textless} 2.2 \backslashtimes 10{\^{}}{\{}-10{\}}{\$}, translates to a conservative limit of {\$}G\backslashmu{\textless}3.3\backslashtimes 10{\^{}}{\{}-8{\}}{\$} - a factor of 4 better than the joint Planck and high-{\$}l{\$} CMB data from other experiments.},
